message: "If you use B(e)arrier Academy, please cite it as below."
title: "B(e)arrier Academy: a kids' safety game for saying exactly where you are"
abstract: >-
  A calm web game for children (ages 6-12) that teaches precise location
  communication in emergencies using a real satellite map, what3words
  three-word addressing, and Morse code, framed around the idea that a good
  emergency message is short but complete (context compression).
